required_variables.value_to_set:
An array of up to two plan IDs. Example update logic:

- const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('task3_comparedPlanIds') || '[]');
- if (plan qualifies and !arr.includes(plan.id) and arr.length < 2) { arr.push(plan.id); localStorage.setItem('task3_comparedPlanIds', JSON.stringify(arr)); }
